  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h3 id=\"children-of-the-sea\">Children of the Sea</h3><p>The Ningyo Clan are a Homebrew Clan By Shanas, Based upon Mermaids and the Japanese Fish-Person Yokai of the same name. Claiming home upon the many Islands of the Land of Water, the Ningyo Clan were the first Shinobi to travel out to sea in search of a Home, and in doing so adapted to the Water in many of the same ways of its inhabitants. Members of the Ningyo Clan are known for being experts at Sound Genjutsu, as the water is such a good conductor of sound waves, and use it to guide ships and communicate with each other across vast distances, and hunt for food. Similarly to the Hoshigaki clan, they also manifest a number of traits of Fish and Sea Life, though rather than being a part of their Biology, are able to use their Chakra to adapt to the various circumstances a Ninja may find themselves in.</p><h4 id=\"ningyo-traits\">Ningyo Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increases:</strong> +2 Char or Wis, +1 Con<br /><strong>Speed:</strong> Your Base Walking Speed is 30ft.<br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Survival, Illusion or Persuasion<br /><strong>Salt-Water Blood:</strong> You have Water Release Affinity and can learn Jutsu with the Water Release Keyword<br /><strong>Fish are Friends, not Food:</strong> You can communicate and understand with Fish and Marine Life, even while underwater</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
